{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16bf7782",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "で、できました……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.2",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "16bf7782",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "この妙薬入りのジュースを飲ませればルミナ様もわたくしに……うふふっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52f75d21",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ついにルミナ様と一線を越える時が来ましたのね……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.4",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "52f75d21",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ああ、想像するだけで……う、鼻血が出てしまいそうです……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3added2a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いけないいけない……妄想はもう卒業しなくては……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.2",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3added2a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "だってこれからは妄想が現実に……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.5",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "3added2a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "はぁ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "afd76392",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんだ？　キッチンから灯りが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.2",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "afd76392",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もう深夜なのに誰か起きているのかな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e44046a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "喉が渇きキッチンに水を飲みに来ると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.2",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9e44046a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ドアの隙間から灯りが漏れていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f5ccb12",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "別に誰がいてもいいか、と特に気にせずにドアを開ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.0",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c3a7d4f2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "雫……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a2962e17",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "──ビクぅっ！？　な、なな、なっ！？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.2",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a2962e17",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ど、どうしてあなたが……！！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.5",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "a2962e17",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ま、まさかずっと見ていましたの！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.0",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "56e7c2e7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "キッチンにいた雫に声を掛けると、妙に慌てた様子を見せる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "214170e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫が何故慌てているのかまったくわからず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.2",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "214170e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "とりあえず水を飲もうと冷蔵庫に近づく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4134649",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こ、こっちに来ないでくださいましっ！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.2",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b4134649",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いったいこんな夜中に何の用ですの！？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.6",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "b4134649",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ま、ま、まさか……よ、夜這いっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e0fad225",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はぁぁっ！？　な、何言ってんだよっ！　そんなことするわけないだろっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bdd53b35",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いいえ！　わたくしは誤魔化されません！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.4",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "bdd53b35",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "その目は夜這いをしに来た、そう言っていますものっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "275d897e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "んな無茶苦茶な……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec869f56",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いつも雫には捲し立てられているが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.2",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ec869f56",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今日はいつにも増して俺に突っかかってくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c6d4e7a4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺は喉乾いたから水飲みに来ただけだって……ん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.2",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c6d4e7a4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ジュースあるじゃん。雫飲まないのか？　だったら俺が貰うぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab1512d1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっと！　何勝手に飲もうとしていますのっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cf33ae9c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ジュースの入っていたコップを掴もうとすると、慌てて奪い取る雫。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f83cf7a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "大事そうに背後にジュース入りのコップを隠し、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.2",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9f83cf7a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ギロリと俺を睨みつけてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e92d521b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんだよ、そんな睨むことないだろっ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.2",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e92d521b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ていうか何でそんなに慌ててんだよ？　そのジュース何かあるのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "92efa74",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "な、ななな、何でもありませんっ！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.2",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "92efa74",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ただのジュースですからっ！！　決してやましいことなど……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "de34df83",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "んー……怪しいな？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.2",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "de34df83",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もしかしてメチャクチャ高級なジュースとかだったり？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.4",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "de34df83",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それで夜な夜な一人でこっそり楽しもうと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5ea8fb5",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "そんなわけありませんっ！　至ってフツーのジュースですっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.4",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "b5ea8fb5",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ただわたくしも喉が渇いていて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.6",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "b5ea8fb5",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "そう、今から飲もうとしていたんですっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eae0fcd4",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あーっ！　叫んだら喉が渇きましたっ！　ゴクゴクゴクっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a91e710d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あああーーーーっ！？　し、しまった……！！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.2",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a91e710d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "つい勢いで飲んでしまいました……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d0bd0688",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "は、謀りましたねっ！？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.3",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "d0bd0688",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "この卑怯者……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c25b3899",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんだよっ！　俺何もしてないだろっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.2",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c25b3899",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そもそも謀ったとかなんだよっ？　やっぱそのジュース何かあったのか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c8d5ee3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "べ、べべ、別に何も……ただのリンゴジュー……うっ？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.4",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "2c8d5ee3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "うあ……あ、あぁっ……効き目が……ううううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e97f0cc0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、おい？　ど、どうしたんだよ？　大丈夫か？　汗すごいぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d173b50d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こ、これ……想像より、効き目が……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.4",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "d173b50d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……ダメ、ダメ……あああ……♥　ガマンが……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3f55ddfc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うわぁぁっ！？　お、おいっ！？　なんだよ！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.2",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3f55ddfc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いきなり押し倒して……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.4",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "3f55ddfc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "って！　おい！　何服脱がそうとしてんだっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ad4d04ed",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "う、うるさいです……！♥　だ、黙っていてくださいっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.0",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d3a650d5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "や、やめろっ！　おい！　本当に脱がすなってぇぇっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "22a44d7f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うう！　お前何考えて……よ、夜這いしてきたのはお前の方じゃないか！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27daa145",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は顔を真っ赤にしながら俺の服を脱がすと、肉棒をそっと掴む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.0",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "217be969",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いきなりの雫の行動にただただ困惑し、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.2",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "217be969",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何もできずに雫のされるがままになってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "176.0",
      "line_index": 176,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86368a0f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ち、違います……！♥　これは、その……事故のようなもので……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "176.2",
      "line_index": 176,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "86368a0f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしの意思ではないのです……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5afb66",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "だからヘンな勘違いはしないように……！♥　わかりましたねっ！？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.0",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f303687a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何わけのわからないことを……うあっ！？　く、うう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ddf49e5a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は俺を睨みながらぺろぺろと乳首を舐め始め、思わず声が漏れ出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "49cc30bc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "行動と言動が全然噛み合っていない様子に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "49cc30bc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いったい雫の身に何が起きているのかまったくわからなくなってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3ac9ec27",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こんなに勃起させて……なんてハレンチな人……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.2",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3ac9ec27",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "恥を知りなさい……♥　このヘンタイ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f8a21e1f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お前が乳首舐めるからだろ……ううっ！　ちょ！　吸うなって……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1214e54f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "なんて熱いおちんちん……♥　こんな汚らわしいモノにルミナ様は……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.0",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b33ae33",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う……うう……！　雫……や、やめろって……うぅ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "208.0",
      "line_index": 208,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "92a20371",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は乳首を舐め回しながら、小さな手で肉棒を扱き始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.0",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16a663cc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "リズミカルに陰茎を擦られ、ぞわぞわした快感に腰が震えあがる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "212.0",
      "line_index": 212,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f80f87f7",
      "speaker": "雫",
